&lt;p&gt;In order to reproduce, implement Hibernate Search and make sure that the java user does not have write permissions on the index directory.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The actual error that occurs will be&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Caused by: org.hibernate.search.SearchException: Unable to create index directory: h:\java\projects\indexDir\nl.myproject.model.Offer for index nl.myproject.model.Offer&lt;br/&gt;
