&lt;p&gt;I am pretty sure, this was working some time ago, but could not find the point in time, where this behavior changed. Am I wrong in assuming that commit &lt;a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/00a69394e69a7a2944b2fd1d611faa958cf42f37" class="external-link" rel="nofollow"&gt;00a6939&lt;/a&gt; in Spring Core has something to do with this behavior?&lt;/p&gt;

