&lt;p&gt;In Spring 4.2, markdown files were responded with correct content type.&lt;br/&gt;
In Spring 4.3RC1, markdown files are delivered back with json contenttype which leads to an error in the browser which tries to parse it as json and fails.&lt;/p&gt;

