&lt;p&gt;THIS BUG LIES IN SPRING 2.5 AND HIGHER&lt;br/&gt;
--------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Dynamic language support is added to Spring by using the &lt;tt&gt;&amp;lt;lang:&amp;gt;&lt;/tt&gt; namespace.&lt;br/&gt;
For eg. for a groovy script, the following xml should handle dynamic language support in Spring.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p/&gt;
&lt;div id="syntaxplugin" class="syntaxplugin" style="border: 1px dashed #bbb; border-radius: 5px !important; overflow: auto; max-height: 30em;"&gt;
&lt;table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em !important; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: black;"&gt;
		&lt;tbody &gt;
				&lt;tr id="syntaxplugin_code_and_gutter"&gt;
						&lt;td  style=" line-height: 1.4em !important; padding: 0em; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
					&lt;pre style="font-size: 1em; margin: 0 10px;  margin-top: 10px;   width: auto; padding: 0;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;"&gt;&amp;lt;lang:groovy id="refreshableMessenger" &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
				&lt;tr id="syntaxplugin_code_and_gutter"&gt;
						&lt;td  style=" line-height: 1.4em !important; padding: 0em; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
					&lt;pre style="font-size: 1em; margin: 0 10px;   width: auto; padding: 0;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;"&gt;    script-source="classpath:org/fw/scripting/groovy/Messenger.groovy"&amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
				&lt;tr id="syntaxplugin_code_and_gutter"&gt;
						&lt;td  style=" line-height: 1.4em !important; padding: 0em; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
					&lt;pre style="font-size: 1em; margin: 0 10px;   width: auto; padding: 0;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;"&gt;    &amp;lt;lang:property name="message" value="Hello World!"/&amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
