&lt;p&gt;The first few lines of my context.xml file are now as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;context:annotation-config /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;context:load-time-weaver /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
