&lt;a href="http://localhost:8080/testmeonce" class="external-link" rel="nofollow"&gt;http://localhost:8080/testmeonce&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test URL2 - Has error and throws exception resulting in empty 500 response:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href="http://localhost:8080/testmetwice" class="external-link" rel="nofollow"&gt;http://localhost:8080/testmetwice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

