&lt;p&gt;I'm trying to map root paths with and without trailing slash to one method in controller, but mapping fails on URL without trailing slash. In this case &lt;tt&gt;PATH_WITHIN_HANDLER_MAPPING_ATTRIBUTE&lt;/tt&gt; equals to servlet path.&lt;/p&gt;

