&lt;p&gt;It would be better if this div would not be created because it is unnecessary (and can cause layout issues).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;UriComponents.Type.QUERY_PARAM does not match spec, in particular it does not allow the relatively common usage of "&amp;#43;" to encode " " (SPACE).  So you get a nasty error with &lt;tt&gt;ServletUriComponentsBuilder.fromRequest&lt;/tt&gt; whenever the query is (legally) encoded with "&amp;#43;" for " ".  An ugly workaround is to do this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p/&gt;
&lt;div id="syntaxplugin" class="syntaxplugin" style="border: 1px dashed #bbb; border-radius: 5px !important; overflow: auto; max-height: 30em;"&gt;
&lt;table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em !important; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: black;"&gt;
		&lt;tbody &gt;
				&lt;tr id="syntaxplugin_code_and_gutter"&gt;
						&lt;td  style=" line-height: 1.4em !important; padding: 0em; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
					&lt;pre style="font-size: 1em; margin: 0 10px;  margin-top: 10px;   width: auto; padding: 0;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;"&gt;UriComponents uri = ServletUriComponentsBuilder.fromRequest(request).replaceQuery(request.getQueryString().replace("+",  "%20")).build(true);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
				&lt;tr id="syntaxplugin_code_and_gutter"&gt;
						&lt;td  style=" line-height: 1.4em !important; padding: 0em; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
					&lt;pre style="font-size: 1em; margin: 0 10px;   width: auto; padding: 0;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;"&gt;String query = uri.getQuery().replace("%20", "+");&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
				&lt;tr id="syntaxplugin_code_and_gutter"&gt;
						&lt;td  style=" line-height: 1.4em !important; padding: 0em; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
					&lt;pre style="font-size: 1em; margin: 0 10px;   margin-bottom: 10px;  width: auto; padding: 0;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Bitstream Vera Sans Mono', 'Courier New', Courier, monospace !important;"&gt;return ServletUriComponentsBuilder.fromUri(uri.toUri()).replaceQuery(query).build(true).toString();&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
			&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
			&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p/&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should be fixed by:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/pull/956" class="external-link" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/pull/956&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
but one test failed:&lt;/p&gt;
